OL,3,CRobison urges UK Government to
OL,4,C'finally step up' and support Glasgow
OL,5,Cafter fire
OL,7,FScotland's Finance Secretary has
OL,8,Fdemanded the UK Government "finally
OL,9,Fstep up" and provide financial support
OL,10,Fto Glasgow following the devastating
OL,11,Fcity centre fire.
OL,13,FShona Robison said it is "astonishing"
OL,14,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,15,F"so far done nothing" to support those
OL,16,Faffected by the blaze at Union Corner.
OL,18,F"Yet again, Scotland's biggest city is
OL,19,Fleft as an afterthought by Labour,"
OL,20,Fshe said, ahead of a meeting with the
OL,21,FTreasury on Thursday.
