OL,3,CRobison urges UK Government to
OL,4,C'finally step up' and support Glasgow
OL,5,Cafter fire
OL,7,FThe Scottish Government announced a
OL,8,F#10 million recovery support package
OL,9,Ffor the area, including cash for the
OL,10,Fbusinesses previously housed in the
OL,11,Fbuilding.
OL,13,FMinisters at Holyrood will also
OL,14,Fprovide up to #1 million to help with
OL,15,Fdemolition costs, as well as uprating
OL,16,Fthe non-domestic rates hardship relief
OL,17,Ffrom 75% to 95%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
