OL,3,CRobison urges UK Government to
OL,4,C'finally step up' and support Glasgow
OL,5,Cafter fire
OL,7,F"As the First Minister set out, the
OL,8,FSNP Government is delivering real
OL,9,Fsupport after the fire devastated
OL,10,Fbusinesses in the heart of the city
OL,11,Fcentre, causing significant disruption
OL,12,Ffor people and impacting their
OL,13,Flivelihoods.
OL,15,F"It is frankly astonishing that Keir
OL,16,FStarmer has so far done nothing to
OL,17,Fsupport Glasgow ` yet again,
OL,18,FScotland's biggest city is left as an
OL,19,Fafterthought by Labour.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
