OL,3,CRobison urges UK Government to
OL,4,C'finally step up' and support Glasgow
OL,5,Cafter fire
OL,7,F"The SNP Government will always do
OL,8,Feverything in our power to make
OL,9,FGlasgow flourish ` and it is time for
OL,10,Fthe UK Government to step up."
OL,12,FSpeaking to the Herald on Monday,
OL,13,FGlasgow City Council leader Susan
OL,14,FAitken said: "The fire at Union Street
OL,15,Fwas still burning when the First
OL,16,FMinister reached out to assure me that
OL,17,FGlasgow would not be expected to deal
OL,18,Fwith an incident with clear national
OL,19,Fimpact on its own.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@^O]vD@NOU
