OL,3,CRobison urges UK Government to
OL,4,C'finally step up' and support Glasgow
OL,5,Cafter fire
OL,7,F"The support the city is receiving
OL,8,Ffrom the Scottish Government is both
OL,9,Fsignificant and very welcome.
OL,10,FOfficials met with civil servants this
OL,11,Fmorning to press for the UK Government
OL,12,Fto match that commitment."
OL,14,FThe UK Government has been approached
OL,15,Ffor comment.
